20mortgage%20rates%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20down%20further%20from%20their%2024-year%20highs%20last%20year.%20Mortgage%20rates%20have%20already%20started%20trending%20downwards%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20and%20they're%20likely%20to%20drop%20further%20if%20the%20Fed%20makes%20multiple%20rate%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20one%20piece%20of%20the%20housing%20crisis%20puzzle%2C%20don't%20expect%20mortgage-rate%20relief%20to%20fix%20the%20locked-up%20housing%20market%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow's%20Chief%20Economist%20Skylar%20Olsen.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20mortgage%20rates%20won't%20alleviate%20the%20housing%20market's%20underlying%20issues%20of%20affordability%20and%20inadequate%20supply%2C%20Olsen%20says.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20thinks%20falling%20mortgage%20rates%20could%20have%20a%20long-term%20effect%20of%20locking%20up%20the%20housing%20market%20even%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20a%20decrease%20in%20mortgage%20rates%20has%20no%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Olsen's%20view%2C%206.2%25%20is%20the%20sweet%20spot%20that%20makes%20homeownership%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20average%20American.%20Once%20mortgage%20rates%20reach%20that%20level%2C%20the%20monthly%20costs%20of%20buying%20and%20renting%20become%20comparable.%20A%20mid-6%25%20mortgage%20rate%20also%20puts%20the%20average%20monthly%20housing%20cost%20at%20a%20third%20of%20overall%20income%2C%20which%20is%20a%20common%20affordability%20benchmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year%20fixed%20mortgage%20rate%20has%20inched%20down%20to%206.35%25%2C%20according%20to%20Freddie%20Mac%2C%20signaling%20that%20the%20housing%20market%20is%20approaching%20that%20zone%20of%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMortgage%20rate%20relief%20over%20August%20could%20return%20that%20middle%20income%20to%20the%20housing%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Olsen%20said%20about%20the%20downward%20move%20in%20rates%20in%20an%20August%2027%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f5a868f-2f73-4564-b5b5-093cfba4ee66%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELower%20mortgage%20rates%20won't%20solve%20everything%2C%20and%20they%20might%20even%20make%20the%20situation%20worse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20quite%20a%20few%20caveats%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlsen%20isn't%20confident%20that%20mortgage%20rates%20will%20drop%20much%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20we%20might%20have%20seen%20most%20of%20the%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20Olsen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%202024%2C%20Olsen%20and%20other%20housing%20economists%20estimated%20that%20mortgage%20rates%20could%20settle%20down%20at%20around%205.5%25.%20But%20now%2C%20experts%20are%20saying%20that%20a%20long-term%20rate%20of%20around%206%25%20is%20more%20probable.%20After%20the%20Fed%20meeting%20in%20Jackson%20Hole%20last%20month%2C%20Olsen%20pointed%20out%20that%20markets%20have%20already%20priced%20in%20a%20rate%20cut.%20That%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20an%20election%20year%2C%20makes%20it%20unlikely%20for%20mortgage%20rates%20to%20decline%20drastically%20going%20forward.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20economy%20starts%20cooling%20faster%20than%20expected%2C%20the%20Fed%20could%20cut%20rates%20more%20aggressively%2C%20bringing%20mortgage%20rates%20down%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20while%20a%20decrease%20in%20mortgage%20rates%20will%20help%20unlock%20buyers%2C%20especially%20the%20middle-income%20buyer%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20homeownership%2C%20it%20won't%20do%20much%20for%20many%20homeowners%2C%20according%20to%20Olsen.%20Existing%20homeowners%20who%20bought%20their%20homes%20at%20lower%20mortgage%20rates%20will%20be%20hesitant%20to%20sell%20in%20a%20higher%20mortgage-rate%20environment%2C%20especially%20if%20rates%20aren't%20slated%20to%20decrease%20much%20more%20from%20current%20levels.%20If%20more%20people%20are%20able%20to%20afford%20houses%20but%20existing%20owners%20aren't%20selling%2C%20then%20the%20housing%20market%20will%20remain%20frozen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20sense%2C%20lower%20mortgage%20rates%20could%20actually%20dry%20up%20housing%20supply%20even%20faster%20and%20send%20home%20prices%20skyrocketing%20again%2C%20according%20to%20Olsen.%20Housing%20inventory%20levels%20have%20been%20increasing%2C%20but%20recently%20unlocked%20homebuyers%20are%20likely%20to%20quickly%20harvest%20existing%20inventory%20and%20return%20the%20housing%20market%20to%20a%20locked-up%20state%2C%20in%20Olsen's%20view.%20This%20effect%20will%20be%20amplified%20if%20rates%20fall%20further%2C%20according%20to%20Olsen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20mortgage%20rate%20relief%20might%20temporarily%20open%20up%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20but%20any%20relief%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20short-lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20inventory%20would%20really%20struggle%20to%20rise%20again%20and%20prices%20could%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20Olsen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20issues%20point%20to%20an%20underlying%20problem%20of%20insufficient%20housing%20supply%20across%20the%20country%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Olsen%20sees%20the%20need%20for%20increased%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-down-payment-assistance-plan-25000-housing-crisis-affordability-zillow-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupply-side%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20stimulate%20construction%20and%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20available%20housing%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20don't%20bank%20on%20lower%20mortgage%20rates%20to%20unlock%20the%20housing%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flower-mortgage-rates-locked-up-housing-market-crisis-home-zillow-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726047002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e05aaca0ff598b26661f3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22