-b9d6-4af9-92b2-54bf68aa88af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20we%20didn't%20pay%20income%20tax%20in%20Dubai%2C%20we%20also%20needed%20to%20understand%20the%20US%20tax%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20certainly%20an%20adjustment%20after%20living%20in%20Dubai%20for%20so%20long.%20We%20also%20needed%20to%20create%20a%20plan%20to%20build%20up%20our%20credit%20score%2C%20which%20included%20getting%20credit%20cards%20and%20opening%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApartments%20in%20New%20York%20City%20are%20more%20expensive%20than%20in%20Dubai.%20We%20had%20an%20apartment%20in%20Dubai%2C%20which%20we%20sold%20before%20we%20moved.%20We%20paid%20triple%20in%20New%20York%20for%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20space%20we%20had%20in%20Dubai.%20As%20we%20didn't%20have%20a%20credit%20score%20in%20the%20US%2C%20some%20landlords%20wouldn't%20rent%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20had%20to%20ensure%20we%20lived%20in%20the%20school%20zone%20for%20the%20school%20we%20wanted%20to%20send%20our%20kids%20to.%20Yet%2C%20while%20housing%20was%20more%20expensive%2C%20schooling%20was%20free.%20As%20expats%2C%20we%20had%20to%20pay%20for%20schooling%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20arrived%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20an%20apartment%20in%20the%20Upper%20West%20Side%20as%20the%20area%20has%20really%20good%20schools%2C%20but%20then%20we%20decided%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20city%20to%20get%20more%20space.%20We%20now%20have%20a%20four-bedroom%20house%20with%20a%20backyard%20for%20the%20boys%20to%20play%20in%2030%20minutes%20outside%20the%20city.%20They%20saw%20snow%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20New%20York%20and%20loved%20building%20snowmen%20in%20the%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d70a8ab-fa35-4fa9-a3cd-b6a8e79018d2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20nicest%20things%20about%20living%20in%20the%20city%20is%20its%20walkability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20weekday%2C%20I%20walk%20the%20kids%20to%20school.%20When%20I%20get%20home%2C%20I%2