%20because%20you%20save%20time%20on%20the%20commute%2C%20but%20we%20still%20get%20time%20in%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJiang%20is%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeek.money%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPeek%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20personal%20finance%20platform%20that%20tracks%20your%20net%20worth.%20It%20launched%20in%20early%202024%20and%20she%20leads%20a%20team%20of%20eight%20employees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sherry%20jiang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4e7761aa2ac29ee32a14a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJiang%20left%20Google%20in%202021%20to%20pursue%20a%20more%20entrepreneurial%20career.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sherry%20Jiang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20firing%20up%20her%20laptop%2C%20she%20makes%20time%20for%20the%20gym.%20This%20is%20a%20relatively%20new%20part%20of%20her%20daily%20routine%2C%20and%20something%20she%20used%20to%20think%20was%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20time%20for%20as%20a%20startup%20founder.%20However%2C%20signing%20up%20for%20a%20fitness%20competition%20with%20her%20friends%20in%202024%20%26quot%3Bforced%20me%20to%20train%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jiang.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20actually%20made%20me%20realize%20I%20could%20wake%20up%20at%207%2C%20squeeze%20in%20a%20workout%20before%20work%2C%20and%20hit%20my%20computer%20at%209%3A30.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20said%20it%20helps%20that%20her%20gym%20is%20within%20walking%20distance%20of%20her%20apartment%2C%20so%20she%20%26quot%3Breally%20doesn't%20have%20an%20excuse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2032-year-old%20hasn't%20always%20prioritized%20things%20like%20sleep%20and%20exercise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Csp