l%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20try%20to%20create%20this%20space%20where%20the%20users%20feel%20like%20they%20can%20tell%20me%20about%20anything%20related%20to%20the%20product%20and%20I%20get%20feedback%20really%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20has%20active%20chats%20with%20hundreds%20of%20users%20and%20is%20responding%20to%20up%20to%2050%20messages%20a%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bit%20insane%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20admitted.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20really%20learn%20so%20much%20about%20your%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20when%20they're%20disappointed%2C%20when%20they%20feel%20successful%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20me%2C%20that's%20more%20important%20than%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20majority%2C%20about%2085%25%2C%20of%20her%20customers%20are%20based%20in%20Asia%2C%20but%20about%2015%25%20are%20US-based.%20She%20sets%20aside%20one%20day%20a%20week%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20her%20US-based%20customers%2C%20who%20are%20anywhere%20from%2012%20to%2015%20hours%20behind%20Singapore.%20Having%20worked%20on%20a%20globally%20distributed%20team%20at%20Google%2C%20Jiang%20is%20used%20to%20juggling%20time%20zone%20differences%20and%20taking%20early-morning%20or%20late-night%20calls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20doing%20this%20since%202016%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20ways%20to%20protect%20your%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20likes%20to%20carve%20out%20time%20for%20herself%20between%206%20p.m.%20and%208%20p.m.%20to%20go%20out%20for%20dinner%20or%20do%20something%20not%20related%20to%20work%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20as%20long%20as%20a%20call%20happens%20after%20that%2C%20I%20still%20get%20my%20protected%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22698%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sherry%20jiang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ce16a31aa2ac29ee34af9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22995%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJiang%20graduated%20from%20UC%20Berkeley%20in%202014.%20Her%20first%20job%20was%20at%20Amazon.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sherry%20Jiang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJiang%20also%20dedicates%20a%20portion%20of%20her%20day%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fsherrypeek%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eposting%20on%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20she's%20built%20a%20network%20of%20more%20than%2018%2C000%20followers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20actually%20how%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20leads%2C%20through%20my%20socials%2C%20so%20I%20post%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20this%20particular%20Thursday%20in%20August%2C%20she%20spent%20some%20time%20prepping%20for%20a%20team%20meeting%20that%20focused%20on%20onboarding%3A%20how%20to%20get%20people%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20app%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20subscribe%20to%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20having%20meetings%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20meetings%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jiang.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20try%20to%20optimize%20our%20time%20together%20in%20person%2C%20and%20deep%20dive%20into%20problems%20that%20are%20more%20efficiently%20solved%20when%20we're%20in%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20general%2C%20she%20says%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Bway%20fewer%20meetings%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20startup%20founder%20than%20she%20did%20in%20the%20corporate%20world.%20%26quot%3BThe%20problem-solving%20per%20hour%20I%20have%20is%20a%20lot%20higher%20in%20a%20startup%20environment%20because%20I'm%20spending%20less%20time%20on%20coordination%20and%20admin.%20It's%20a%20lot%20more%20of%20just%20rolling%20your%20sleeves%20up%20and%20executing%2C%20versus%20spending%20time%20thinking%20about%20what%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20works%20late%20most%20weeknights.%20After%20her%206%20to%208%20p.m.%20break%2C%20she%20spends%20the%20evenings%20doing%20administrative%20tasks%2C%20answering%20emails%2C%20and%20catching%20up%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThis%20works%20for%20me%20but%20I%20think%20everybody%20has%20a%20different%20way%20they%20structure%20their%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jiang.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227512fee5-bcbc-4fca-9d31-c0499e7402a0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESetting%20boundaries%3A%20'Date%20night'%20on%20Thursdays%20and%20no-work%20Saturdays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20feel%20like%20she's%20ever%20off%20the%20clock.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20remind%20myself%20that%20with%20your%20own%20startup%2C%20the%20work%20never%20ends%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jiang.%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20have%20to%20create%20the%20boundaries%20yourself%3B%20you%20can't%20just%20let%20the%20boundaries%20happen%20based%20on%20the%20work%20that%20is%20always%20going%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20it's%20%26quot%3Binevitable%26quot%3B%20to%20carry%20your%20startup%20with%20you%20wherever%20you%20go%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20also%20think%20there%20is%20a%20balance%3A%20It's%20OK%20to%20have%20the%20gears%20be%20grinding%20but%20you%20also%20have%20to%20be%20super%20deliberate%20about%20setting%20aside%20time%20to%20not%20think%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20that%20reason%2C%20Jiang%20protects%20her%20Saturdays.%20Unless%20there's%20a%20special%20circumstance%2C%20like%20fundraising%20for%20the%20company%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20work%20on%20Friday%20nights%2C%20and%20I%20really%20try%20not%20to%20work%20on%20Saturdays%2C%20so%20I%20have%20that%2024%20hours%20where%20I'm%20just%20doing%20something%20else.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20doesn't%20mind%20working%20on%20Sundays.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20having%20that%20time%20to%20do%20deep%20work%20and%20think%20about%20solving%20problems.%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20space%20to%20do%20it%20during%20the%20week%20because%20I'm%20getting%20bombarded%20with%20a%20ton%20of%20things%20in%20all%20different%20directions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20fun%20work%20in%20a%20way%20%E2%80%94%20things%20that%20are%20intellectually%20stimulating.%20I%20get%20to%20sit%20down%20and%20think%20about%20it%20for%20hours%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20uninterrupted%20by%20other%20things%20happening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJiang%20and%20her%20partner%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20startup%20founder%2C%20also%20block%20out%20one%20night%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20Thursday%20%E2%80%94%20to%20set%20work%20aside%20and%20%26quot%3Bjust%20hang%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20rule%20is%20we%20can%20talk%20about%20anything%20but%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20appears%20to%20be%20at%20least%20one%20exception%20to%20the%20Thursday%20date%20night%20rule%3A%20Talking%20to%20a%20Business%20Insider%20reporter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-of-startup-founder-ceo-in-singapore-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726045202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4e5f15da406397bf74d67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-of-startup-founder-ceo-in-singapore-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20remind%20myself%20that%20with%20your%20own%20startup%2C%20the%20work%20never%20ends.%20So%20you%20have%20to%20create%20the%20boundaries%20yourself.%26qu