ets%20me%20record%20100s%20of%20hours%20of%20live%20sports%20and%20other%20great%20content.%20For%20big%20games%2C%20I%20start%20playing%20the%20recordings%20about%20one-third%20of%20the%20way%20though%20(while%20carefully%20avoiding%20spoilers%20on%20social%20media).%20Then%2C%20when%20ads%20appear%2C%20I%20just%20forward%20through%20them%20all.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20game%20is%20almost%20over%2C%20I'm%20up%20with%20the%20live%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20the%20only%20one%20who's%20caught%20on%20to%20this%20incredible%20deal.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcord-cutting-intentions-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecord-cutting%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20crushing%20the%20cable%20and%20satellite%20industries%2C%20OTA%20TV%20viewing%20is%20holding%20on%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20strong%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivicscience.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECivicScience%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20leading%20research%20and%20survey%20company%2C%20started%20tracking%20OTA%20TV%20antenna%20usage%20and%20demographics%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20most%20surprising%20finding%20is%20that%20younger%20viewers%20are%20heavier%20users%20of%20digital%20TV%20antennas.%20(I%20thought%20young%20people%20would%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20own%20a%20pet%20armadillo%20than%20an%20old-school%20antenna.%20I%20was%20wrong).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Ft65c7%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Digital%20TV%20antenna%20ownership%20by%20generation%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22477%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ECivicScience%20research%20has%20also%20found%20that%20this%20OTA%20TV%20audience%20is%20more%20tech-savvy.%20That's%20another%20counter-intuitive%20datapoint%