eature%20will%20make%20taking%200.5x%20selfies%2C%20a%20Gen%20Z-beloved%20photo-taking%20method%2C%20way%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E0.5x%20selfies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F06%2F23%2Ftechnology%2F0-5-selfie.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20the%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F06%2F23%2Ftechnology%2F0-5-selfie.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erage%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20Gen%20Z.%20Taking%20one%20involves%20adjusting%20the%20iPhone%20camera%20to%20the%200.5x%20zoom%20setting%2C%20flipping%20the%20phone%20around%2C%20and%20then%20pressing%20the%20volume%20button%20to%20take%20a%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20camera%20setting%20also%20allows%20users%20to%20capture%20a%20large%20group%20of%20people%20or%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20subject's%20environment%2C%20which%20a%20regular%20front-camera%20selfie%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20and%20marketing%20experts%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20the%20new%20additions%20to%20the%20iPhone%2016%20are%20likely%20to%20resonate%20with%20younger%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20regards%20to%20whether%20the%20new%20Camera%20Control%20feature%20was%20designed%20with%20the%20Gen%20Z%20generation%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20think%20the%20simple%20one-word%20answer%20to%20that%20is%20'absolutely%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Monica%20Hillison%2C%20a%20marketing%20professor%20from%20Virginia%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHillison%20added%20that%20the%20function%20will%20work%20well%20with%20other%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%20or%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20think%20of%20the%20Camera%20Control%20feature%20as%20something%20that%20a%20third-party%20tool%20like%20Instagram%2C%20ChatGPT%20or%20Google%20can%20also%20potentially%20access%20and%20use%20to%20complement%20their%20own%20new%20tech%20developments%20such%20as%20AI%20features%2C%26quot%3B%20Hillison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbdul%20A