r%20venture%20%E2%80%98MeenGurry%20Memories%E2%80%99%20(%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emeen%20gurry%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20means%20fish%20curry)%2C%20as%20a%20homage%20to%20their%20shared%20memories%20around%20the%20dining%20table.%20Every%20weekend%2C%20she%20curated%20different%20meal%20boxes%20while%20continuing%20her%20job%20during%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20running%20MeenGurry%20Memories%2C%20Reshma%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20do%20something%20to%20promote%20chefs%20like%20her%20mother%20Uma%20and%20aunt%20Lakshmi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reshma%20with%20her%20freshly%20made%20banana%20chips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840.jpeg%20960w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365474%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EReshma%20with%20her%20freshly%20made%20banana%20chips.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sister%20duo%2C%20Uma%20and%20Lakshmi%2C%20had%20participated%20in%20a%20cooking%20contest%20on%20a%20TV%20channel%20called%20%E2%80%98Mazhavil%20Manorama%E2%80%99%20in%202019.%20They%20were%20among%20the%20semi-finalists%2C%20which%20was%20a%20huge%20motivation%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20immense%20potential%20for%20people%20like%20our%20parents%20who%20are%20retired%20or%20living%20alone.%20They%20need%20to%20be%20engaged.%20I%20then%20asked%20my%20mother%20to%20make%20her%20famous%20prawn%20and%20mango%20pickle%2C%20a%20childhood%20favourite%20of%20many.%20I%20packaged%20it%20and%20started%20selling%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Reshma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Emulga%20podi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(gun%20powder)%2C%20%3Cem%3Esambar%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%2C%20and%20other%20products%20were%20also%20introduced.%20Reshma%2C%20an%20MBA%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20then%20created%20a%20platform%20to%20sell%20these%20nostalgic%20products%2C%20naming%20it%20%E2%80%98Tocco%E2%80%99.%20The%20name%2C%20short%20for%20%E2%80%98The%20Orange%20Candy%20Co%E2%80%99%2C%20made%20sense%20because%2C%20for%20Reshma%2C%20the%20ultimate%20symbol%20of%20nostalgia%20was%20the%20orange%20candies%20she%20shared%20with%20her%20sister%20during%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Tocco%2C%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20pack%20this%20childhood%20nostalgia%20in%20a%20box%20for%20other%20people%20to%20enjoy.%20In%20late%202022%2C%20she%20quit%20her%20job%20to%20fully%20focus%20on%20building%20the%20platform.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20onboarding%20the%20first%20two%20chefs%2C%20Reshma%20brought%20in%20more%2C%20expanding%20the%20platform%20to%20include%20over%2016%20chefs%20from%20different%20cities%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%20They%20offer%20snacks%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20jackfruit%20chips%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshankarpali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20sweet%20snack)%3Cem%3E%2C%20masalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20sambar%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%20podi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powder)%2C%20pickles%20like%20prawn%2C%20cut%20mango%2C%20homemade%20curd%20chilli%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epuli%20inji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(ginger%20pickle)%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2058-year-old%20Uma%20Suresh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20cooking%20since%20she%20was%20in%20Class%206%2C%20Tocco%20has%20given%20new%20meaning%20to%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CCooking%20is%20my%20passion.%20I%20would%20always%20pack%20some%20pickles%20for%20anyone%20who%20came%20home.%20I%20always%20dreamed%20of%20running%20a%20business%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to.%20Thanks%20to%20my%20daughters%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20made%20a%20name%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Uma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20MeenGurry%20Memories%20(%40meengurry_memories)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Uma%20and%20her%20sister%20Lakshmi%20embarked%20on%20trips%20to%20Dubai%20and%20Goa%20using%20their%20own%20earnings!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavana%20Shah%2C%2051%2C%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20who%20makes%20snacks%20and%20starters%20and%20runs%20cooking%20classes%2C%20says%20Tocco%20has%20given%20her%20a%20renewed%20sense%20of%20vigour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWork%20is%20very%20important%20for%20women%20over%2050%2C%20especially%20when%20going%20through%20menopause.%20Dealing%20with%20the%20hot%20flashes%20and%20mood%20swings%20is%20easier%20when%20we%20are%20busy.%20While%20I%20had%20regular%20customers%20in%20Vile%20Parle%2C%20Tocco%20has%20helped%20people%20across%20the%20country%20discover%20who%20I%20am.%20I%20thank%20Reshma%20for%20giving%20me%20a%20new%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhavana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20also%20offers%20flexibility%20to%20chefs%20like%20Bhavana%2C%20who%20occasionally%20travels%20abroad%20to%20visit%20her%20children.%20Additionally%2C%20Tocco%20assists%20with%20branding%20and%20marketing%2C%20which%20are%20major%20challenges%20in%20establishing%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%20crore!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reshma%2C%20the%20team%20at%20Tocco%20ensures%20that%20all%20products%20are%20homemade%2C%20carefully%20crafted%20in%20small%20batches%2C%20and%20preservative-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20become%20a%20chef%20at%20Tocco%2C%20one%20must%20apply%20on%20the%20website.%20After%20an%20initial%20call%2C%20the%20top%20three%20dishes%20of%20the%20chef%20are%20discussed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20dishes%20must%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%2