%20even%20help%20with%20getting%20an%20FSSAI%20certification%2C%20in%20case%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Tocco%20receives%20an%20order%2C%20they%20send%20it%20to%20the%20chef%2C%20who%20makes%20the%20dish%20to%20order%20and%20ships%20it.%20The%20platform%20handles%20order%20management%2C%20packing%2C%20shipping%2C%20and%20customer%20care.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20provide%20access%20to%20healthy%2C%20homemade%20food%20for%20busy%20people.%20The%20biggest%20motivation%20is%20seeing%20chefs%20like%20my%20mother%20live%20an%20independent%20life%20thanks%20to%20their%20earnings.%20Many%20of%20them%20would%20not%20have%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20sell%20their%20products%20on%20a%20large%20scale.%20We%20are%20providing%20an%20opportunity%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Tocco%20processes%20over%201%2C000%20orders%20per%20month.%20They%20plan%20to%20onboard%20more%20chefs%20and%20expand%20their%20operations.%20Reshma%20divides%20her%20time%20between%20Mumbai%20and%20Kochi%2C%20where%20she%20has%20set%20up%20a%20facility%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20banana%20chips%2C%20one%20of%20their%20best%20selling%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-500x648.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Bhavana%20baking%20nankhatai.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-500x648.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-232x300.jpeg%20232w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-150x194.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo