e%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20today%20said%20it%20has%20become%20a%20habit%20for%20the%20Congress%20leader%20to%20stand%20with%20%26quot%3Bforces%20that%20conspire%20to%20divide%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStanding%20with%20forces%20that%20conspire%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20and%20making%20anti-national%20statements%20have%20become%20a%20habit%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Whether%20it%20is%20supporting%20the%20JKNC's%20anti-national%20and%20anti-reservation%20agenda%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20or%20making%20anti-India%20statements%20on%20foreign%20platforms%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20always%20threatened%20the%20nation's%20security%20and%20hurt%20sentiments%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EStanding%20with%20forces%20that%20conspire%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20and%20making%20anti-national%20statements%20have%20become%20a%20habit%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Whether%20it%20is%20supporting%20the%20JKNC's%20anti-national%20and%20anti-reservation%20agenda%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20or%20making%20anti-India%20statements%20on%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Shah%20(%40AmitShah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1833746683957813465%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi's%20statement%20lays%20bare%20the%20Congress's%20politics%20of%20causing%20rifts%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20regionalism%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20linguistic%20differences.%20By%20speaking%20about%20abolishing%20reservations%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20once%20again%20brought%20the%20Congress's%20anti-reservation%20face%20to%20the%20forefront.%20The%20thoughts%20that%20were%20in%20his%20mind%20eventually%20found%20their%20way%20out%20as%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20that%20as%20long%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20there%2C%20neither%20can%20anyone%20abolish%20reservations%20nor%20can%20anyone%20mess%20with%20the%20nation's%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20was%20responding%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20at%20an%20interaction%20with%20students%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20in%20the%20US.%20Responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20reservation%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20think%20of%20scrapping%20reservations%20when%20India%20is%20a%20fair%20place%20and%20India%20is%20not%20a%20fair%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20responded%20by%20alleging%20that%20the%20Congress's%20leader%20campaign%20to%20save%20the%20Constitution%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bcharade%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20prejudice%20against%20reservation%20is%20out%20in%20the%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20to%20reservation%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20legacy%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20said%2C%20saying%20that%20former%20prime%20ministers%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20were%20also%20against%20caste-based%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Prasad%20said%20other%20members%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20bloc%20--%20DMK%20chief%20M%20K%20Stalin%2C%20RJD%20supremo%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20leaders%20of%20the%20Left%20parties%20--%20should%20speak%20out%20on%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20warn%20(people)%20that%20if%20the%20Congress%20tries%20to%20tamper%20with%20the%20provision%20of%20reservation%20in%20any%20way%20or%20scrap%20it%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20vehemently%20oppose%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20offensive%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20key%20states%20such%20as%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20backfoot%20after%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20score%20dropped%20this%20time%2C%20wants%20to%20use%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20to%20project%20the%20Opposition%20as%20anti-reservation%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20swing%20voters.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20during%20his%20three-day%20US%20trip%2C%20in%20which%20he%20repeatedly%20targeted%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20parent%2C%20has%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20ruling%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20also%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bfear%20of%20BJP%26quot%3B%20had%20vanished%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20results.%20%26quot%3BWithin%20minutes%20of%20the%20election%20result%2C%20nobody%20was%20scared%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20These%20are%20huge%20achievements%2C%20not%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20or%20Congress%2C%20but%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%20who%20realised%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20accept%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20BJP's%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20knows%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20an%20immature%20and%20part-time%20leader.%20But%20people%20have%20put%20a%20huge%20responsibility%20on%20his%20shoulders%20since%20he%20became%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition.%20But%20I%20feel%20sad%20to%20say%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20a%20black%20spot%20in%20Indian%20democracy.%20He%20does%20not%20even%20know%20what%20to%20talk%20about%20when%20he%20visits%20a%20foreign%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726039080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F1j87nid8_amit-shah-rahul-gandhi-split_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com