f%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%20on%20August%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%20suspects%20that%20Dr%20Ghosh%20and%20his%20wife%20bought%20these%20properties%20with%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%20%26quot%3BThese%20documents%20related%20to%20properties%20were%20seized%20based%20on%20the%20prima%20facie%20suspicion%20that%20those%20properties%20were%20purchased%20out%20of%20Proceeds%20of%20Crime%2C%26quot%3B%20ED%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20found%20that%20Sangeeta%20Ghosh%20bought%20two%20properties%20without%20proper%20approval%20from%20West%20Bengal%20government%20and%20was%20later%20granted%20a%20post%20facto%20approval%20by%20none%20other%20than%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20her%20senior%20at%20work%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20search%2C%20it%20was%20unravelled%20that%20Dr.%20Sangeeta%20Ghosh%20w%2Fo%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20had%20purchased%20two%20immovable%20properties%20without%20any%20proper%20approval%20from%20the%20State%20Government%20Authorities.%20Interestingly%2C%20a%20post%20facto%20approval%20was%20granted%20to%20Dr.%20Sangeeta%20Ghosh%20to%20purchase%20the%20property%20by%20Dr.%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20in%20year%202021.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20Dr.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20Ghosh%20was%20posted%20in%20capacity%20of%20Principal%20of%20R.%20G.%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Dr.%20Sangeeta%20Ghosh%20was%20posted%20there%20as%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ED%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20on%20Friday%20searched%20seven%20premises%20belonging%20to%20Dr%20Ghosh%2C%20his%20close%20relatives%20and%20associates.%20The%20investigation%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20in%20a%20case%20registered%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act.%20The%20ED's%20case%20is%20based%20on%20an%20FIR%20registered%20by%20the%20CBI%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ghosh%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20the%20state-run%20hospital's%20response%20to%20the%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20its%20premises.%20The%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government's%20move%20to%20name%20him%20the%20principal%20of%20a%20medical%20college%20hours%20after%20he%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20top%20post%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20had%20raised%20eyebrows.%20Both%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20questioned%20why%20the%20hospital%20administration%20under%20Dr%20Ghosh%20did%20not%20register%20a%20police%20complaint%20after%20the%20doctor's%20body%20was%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20outrage%20over%20the%20shocking%20incident%2C%20allegations%20of%20large-scale%20corruption%20in%20the%20hospital%20emerged.%20A%20former%20colleague%20of%20Dr%20Ghosh%20approached%20the%20high%20court%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20corruption.%20The%20court%20then%20handed%20over%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20is%20also%20probing%20the%20rape-murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726035300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Frqmidj9_sandip-ghosh_625x300_18_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F4-flats-2-houses-1-farmhouse-sandip-ghoshs-properties-under-the-scanner-6538813%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20flats%2C%20two%20houses%20and%20a%20farmhouse%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20another%20flat%20in%20Murshidabad%20--%20multiple%20properties%20belonging%20to%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20former%20Principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Sangeeta%20are%20under%20the%20scanner%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F4-flats-2-houses-1-farmhouse-sandip-ghoshs-properties-under-the-scanner-6538813%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hyun%20Bin%20gives%20a%20shoutout%20to%20Ye%20Jin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%