C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Prisoner's%20Wife%20Wins%20%245.6%20Million%20In%20Settlement%20For%20Strip%20Search%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20California%20woman%20has%20been%20awarded%20%245.6%20million%20after%20being%20sexually%20assaulted%20during%20a%20strip%20search%20while%20visiting%20her%20husband%20in%20prison.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20in%20September%202019%20at%20a%20correctional%20facility%20in%20Tehachapi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChristina%20Cardenas%2C%20who%20had%20travelled%20four%20hours%20to%20see%20her%20husband%2C%20was%20subjected%20to%20a%20series%20of%20invasive%20searches%2C%20including%20strip%20searches%2C%20drug%20and%20pregnancy%20tests%2C%20and%20medical%20scans.%20During%20one%20of%20these%20procedures%2C%20a%20male%20doctor%20sexually%20assaulted%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20motivation%20in%20pursuing%20this%20lawsuit%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20others%20do%20not%20have%20to%20endure%20the%20same%20egregious%20offences%20that%20I%20experienced%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Cardenas%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fcalifornia-inmate-wife-christina-cardenas-strip-search-settlement-lawyers%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECBS%20News.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%2C%20which%20includes%20contributions%20from%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Corrections%20and%20Rehabilitation%20and%20several%20individual%20defendants%2C%20will%20provide%20Mrs%20Cardenas%20with%20significant%20compensation%20for%20the%20harm%20she%20endured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20highlighted%20the%20excessive%20and%20invasive%20nature%20of%20the%20searches%2C%20which%20were%20conducted%20based%20on%20a%20warrant%20that%20authorized%20strip%20searches%20only%20if%20contraband%20was%20detected%20through%20X-rays%20or%20CT%20scans.%20Despite%20multiple%20scans%20revealing%20no%20evidence%20of%20contraband%2C%20Mrs%20Cardenas%20was%20subjected%20to%20humiliating%20and%20invasive%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20sexual%20assault%2C%20Mrs%20Cardenas%20was%20subjected%20to%20other%20forms%20of%20mistreatment%2C%20including%20being%20denied%20necessities%20like%20water%20and%20bathroom%20use.%20She%20was%20also%20forced%20to%20pay%20exorbitant%20fees%20for%20the%20medical%20procedures%20she%20underwent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Cardenas'%20attorneys%20argued%20that%20the%20prison%20officials'%20actions%20were%20intended%20to%20intimidate%20and%20deter%20her%20from%20visiting%20her%20husband.%20They%20emphasised%20that%20the%20invasive%20searches%20and%20the%20sexual%20assault%20were%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20her%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%20includes%20a%20requirement%20for%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Corrections%20and%20Rehabilitation%20to%20implement%20new%20policies%20to%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20visitors%20who%20are%20subjected%20to%20strip%20searches.%20These%20policies%20will%20ensure%20that%20visitors%20are%20informed%20of%20their%20rights%2C%20that%20searches%20are%20conducted%20respectfully%2C%20and%20that%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20searches%20is%20strictly%20adhered%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726032000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fquqc6ek_christina-cardenas-with-husband-_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-prisoners-wife-who-was-sexually-assaulted-during-strip-search-wins-5-6-million-in-settlement-6538487%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Christina%20Cardenas%20was%20subjected%20to%20a%20series%20of%20invasive%20searches%2C%20including%20strip%20searches%2C%20drug%20and%20pregnancy%20tests%2C%20and%20medical%20scans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-prisoners-wife-who-was-sexually-assaulted-during-strip-search