Was%20Clicked%2C%20Politics%20Happened%26quot%3B%3A%20Vinesh%20Tears%20Into%20PT%20Usha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20who%20had%20a%20heartbreaking%20exit%20from%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20over%20failed%20weigh-in%2C%20has%20made%20an%20explosive%20revelation%20from%20her%20meeting%20with%20PT%20Usha%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Indian%20Olympics%20Association%20(IOA).%20Vinesh%20had%20fallen%20ill%20after%20her%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2053kg%20freestyle%20wrestling%20final%2C%20over%20increased%20weight%2C%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20poly-clinic%20in%20the%20Olympics%20village.%20PT%20Usha%20shared%20a%20picture%20on%20social%20media%20where%20she%20could%20be%20seen%20interacting%20with%20Vinesh%20in%20the%20clinic%2C%20but%20the%20wrestler%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20photo%20was%20clicked%20without%20informing%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%2C%20who%20recently%20joined%20politics%20by%20signing%20up%20with%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20claims%20that%20she%20received%20no%20support%20from%20PT%20Usha%2C%20although%20the%20latter%20claimed%20that%20she%20stood%20with%20the%20heartbroken%20wrestler%20during%20that%20tough%20time%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20support%20I%20got%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinesh%20said%20during%20a%20chat%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMahuaMoitraFans%2Fstatus%2F1833560474689884402%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20news%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BPT%20Usha%20madam%20visited%20me%20at%20the%20hospital.%20One%20photo%20was%20clicked...Like%20you%20said%2C%20in%20politics%20a%20lot%20happens%20behind%20closed%20doors.%20Similarly%2C%20politics%20happened%20there%20(in%20Paris)%20as%20well.%20That's%20why%20I%20was%20heartbroken.%20Otherwise%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20saying%20'don't%20leave%20wrestling'.%20For%20what%20should%20I%20continue%3F%20There%20is%20politics%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%2C%20furious%20with%20PT%20Usha's%20decision%20to%20share%20the%20picture%20on%20social%20media%20claiming%20that%20she%20stands%20in%20support%20of%20the%20wrestler%2C%20said%20that%20this%20wasn't%20the%20right%20way%20to%20show%20support%2C%20and%20was%20mere%20pretension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20on%20a%20hospital%20bed%2C%20where%20you%20don't%20know%20what's%20happening%20in%20life%20outside%2C%20you%20are%20going%20through%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20phases%20of%20your%20life.%20At%20that%20place%2C%20just%20to%20show%20everyone%20you%20are%20standing%20with%20me%2C%20aap%20bina%20bataye%20photo%20kheench%20rahe%20ho%2C%20fir%20social%20media%20pe%20daal%20ke%20bol%20rahe%20ho%20hum%20saath%20mein%20khade%20hain%20(clicked%20a%20photo%20without%20telling%20me%20and%20then%20putting%20it%20on%20social%20media%20to%20say%20you%20are%20standing%20with%20me).%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20how%20you%20show%20support%20(pretending%20to).%20What%20was%20it%20more%20than%20(posturing)!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726031340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Frctmhudg_pt-usha-vinesh_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fclicked-picture-without-telling-me-pretended-to-support-vinesh-phogat-slams-pt-usha-6538128%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20wrestler-turned-politician%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20has%20slammed%20IOA%20president%20PT%20Usha%20for%20'pretending'%20to%20support%20her%20after%20the%20failed%20weigh-in%20incident%20in%20Paris%20Olympics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fclicked-picture-without-telling-me-pretended-to-support-vinesh-phogat-slams-pt-usha-6538128%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jon%20Stewart%20Criticizes%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20Jan.%206%20Response%20During%20Presidential%20Debate%2C%20Praises%20Kamala%20Harris%E2%80%99%20Abortion%20Comments%3A%20%E2%80%98She%20Crushed%20That%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726031223000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FScreen-Shot-2024-07-16-at-12.06.03-PM-e1721146031682.png%3Fw%3D738%26h%3D493%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236140400%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jon%20Stewart%20appeared%20live%20on%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Daily%20Show%E2%80%9D%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20where%20he%20shared%20his%20reaction%20to%20the%20presidential%20debate%20between%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%20The%20show%20played%20dueling%20clips%20of%20Trump%20and%20Harris%E2%80%99%20responses%20to%20abortion%2C%20including%20Trump%20saying%20%E2%80%9Cwe%E2%80%99ve%20gotten%20what%20everybody%20wanted%E2%80%9D%20after%20overturning%20Roe%20v.%20Wade.%20Harris%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Michaela%20Zee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fjon-stewart-donald-trump-kamala-harris-presidential-debate-response-1236140400%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Tables%20Turned%20Between%20Biden%20vs%20Trump%20And%20Harris%20vs%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2028%2C%20shortly%20after%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20faced%20off%20in%20a%20Presidential%20debate%20for%20the%20high-stakes%20US%20election%2C%20many%20concluded%20that%20the%20fight%20was%20over%20even%20before%20it%20began.%20As%20the%2081-year-old%20US%20President%20lost%20his%20train%20of%20thought%20multiple%20times%20while%20speaking%20on%20critical%20subjects%2C%20his%2078-year-old%20predecessor%20and%20opponent%20mocked%20his%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20September%2011%2C%20Trump%20faced%20a%20different%20Democrat%20presidential%20candidate.%20And%20this%20time%2C%20he%20was%20the%20older%20one%20and%20by%20a%20much%20larger%20margin.%20At%2059%2C%20Vice-President%20Kamala%20Harris%20is%20nearly%20two%20decades%20younger%20and%20she%20did%20not%20miss%20an%20opportunity%20to%20drive%20this%20point%20home%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20subtle%20manner.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20do%20offer%20is%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leadership%20for%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20US%20Presidential%20debates%2C%20televised%20and%20followed%20closely%20on%20social%20media%2C%20optics%20matter.%20Where%20Biden%20had%20appeared%20pale%20and%20confused%2C%20Harris%20was%20confident%20and%20focused.%20Harris%20started%20by%20walking%20up%20to%20Trump%20and%20shaking%20his%20hand%2C%20%26quot%3BHi%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20let's%20have%20a%20good%20debate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20handshake%20on%20the%20US%20Presidential%20debate%20stage%20after%20eight%20years.%20It%20was%20underlined%20that%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20two%20leaders%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20debate%20began%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20Indian%20origin%20pulled%20no%20punches.%20On%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20she%20managed%20to%20get%20under%20Trump's%20skin%2C%20setting%20him%20off%20on%20rants%20his%20team%20would%20not%20be%20happy%20about.%20She%20targeted%20him%20over%20his%20convictions%20in%20criminal%20cases%2C%20his%20administration's%20handling%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20his%20image%20on%20the%20global%20scene.%20The%20tables%20had%20turned.%20In%20the%20earlier%20debate%2C%20Biden%20had%20struggled%20to%20counter%20Trump's%20attacks%20on%20his%20policies%2C%20this%20time%20Harris'%20messaging%20was%20crisp%20and%20Trump%20appeared%20to%20be%20defensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20debate%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20US%20economy%20and%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20spoke%20of%20her%20middle-class%20background%20and%20plans%20to%20support%20families%20and%20small%20businesses%20if%20elected%20to%20the%20top%20post.%20Targeting%20Trump%2C%20she%20said%20he%20would%20provide%20tax%20cuts%20to%20%26quot%3Bbillionaires%20and%20big%20corporations%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20has%20no%20plan%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20responded%20with%20a%20personal%20attack.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20a%20Marxist%20-%20everybody%20knows%20she's%20a%20Marxist.%20Her%20father's%20a%20Marxist%20professor%20in%20economics%2C%20and%20he%20taught%20her%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump%20targeted%20Harris%20over%20Biden%20administration's%20immigration%20policies%2C%20she%20responded%20sharply%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20hear%20from%20the%20same%20old%20tired%20playbook%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20lies%2C%20grievances%20and%20name-calling.%26quot%3B%20A%20key%20moment%20in%20the%20debate%20was%20when%20Trump%20rattled%20out%20a%20social%20media%20conspiracy%20theory%20that%20immigrants%20are%20eating%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Springfield%2C%20they're%20eating%20the%20dogs%2C%20the%20people%20that%20came%20in%2C%20they're%20eating%20the%20cats.%20They're%20eating%20the%20pets%20of%20the%20people%20that%20live%20there.%20And%20this%20is%20what's%20happening%20in%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Harris'%20microphone%20was%20off%2C%20but%20she%20was%20seen%20laughing%20and%20mouthing%20%26quot%3Bwhat%3F%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20sharp%20response%20was%20when%20Harris%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BPutin%20would%20be%20sitting%20in%20Kyiv%20with%20his%20eyes%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20Europe%26quot%3B%20if%20Trump%20was%20President.%20She%20also%20said%20Putin%20%26quot%3Bwould%20eat%20you%20for%20lunch%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompare%20these%20exchanges%20to%20the%20ones%20during%20the%20Biden%20vs%20Trump%20debate.%20The%20older%20President%20appeared%20to%20be%20putting%20up%20a%20relatively%20muted%20performance%20and%20struggling%20to%20articulate%20himself%20as%20Trump%20put%20out%20fireworks.%20The%20debate%20was%20still%20underway%20when%20the%20White%20House%20said%20Biden%20was%20suffering%20from%20a%20cold.%20The%20US%20President's%20performance%20did%20not%20help%20his%20attempts%20to%20convince%20the%20nation%20that%20he%20could%20serve%20in%20what%20is%20among%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20positions%20till%2086.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20not%20running%20against%20Biden%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20challenge%20Harris%20faced%20going%20into%20this%20debate%20was%20Team%20Trump's%20push%20to%20tie%20her%20to%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20failure.%20Harris%2C%20however%2C%20responded%20by%20stressing%20that%20she%20represents%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leadership%20and%20that%20it's%20time%20to%20%26quot%3Bturn%20the%20page%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20clearly%20not%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20certainly%20not%20Donald%20Trump.%20And%20what%20I%20do%20offer%20is%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leadership%20for%20our%20country%2C%20one%20who%20believes%20in%20what%20is%20possible.%20One%20who%20brings%20a%20sense%20of%20optimism%20about%20what%20we%20can%20do%20instead%20of%20always%20disparaging%20the%20American%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20point%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20heard%20tonight%2C%20two%20very%20different%20visions%20for%20this%20country.%20One%20that%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20future%20and%20one%20that%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20managed%20to%20irk%20Trump%20by%20saying%20that%20world%20leaders%20laughed%20at%20him%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20a%20disgrace%26quot%3B.%20Trump%20responded%20by%20citing%20close%20ties%20with%20Hungary%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban%20and%20that%20he%20has%20said%20Trump%20should%20return%20as%20President.%20The%20reference%20to%20Orban%2C%20known%20for%20restrictions%20on%20immigration%20and%20gay%20rights%2C%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20Trump's%20continuing%20admiration%20of%20autocratic%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20was%20no%20specific%20mic%20drop%20moment%2C%20the%20debate%20did%20see%20several%20of%20Harris'%20punches%20land%20well.%20The%20November%20election%20is%20still%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20close%20contest%20--%20ABC%20poll%20tracker%20shows%20a%202.8%20percentage%20points%20--%20but%20the%20Democrats%20have%20without%20doubt%20made%20a%20comeback%20from%20where%20they%20were%20during%20the%20June%2028%20Biden%20vs%20Trump%20debate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726030980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmqfp33jg_trump-harris-biden-split_625x300_11_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-debate-kamala-harris-donald-trump-how-tables-turned-between-biden-vs-trump-and-harris-vs-trump-6538351%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20June%2028%2C%20shortly%20after%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20faced%20off%20in%20a%20Presidential%20debate%20for%20the%20high-stakes%20US%20election%2C%20many%20concluded%20that%20the%20fight%20was%20over%20even%20before%20it%20began%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-debate-kamala-harris-donald-trump-how-tables-turned-between-biden-vs-trump-and-harris-vs-trump-6538351%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Girl%20Genitalia%20Mutilated%2C%20Sold%20For%20Magic%20In%20Ivory%20Coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20a%20witch%20doctor%2C%20Moussa%20Diallo%20would%20regularly%20smear%20himself%20in%20a%20lotion%20made%20from%20a%20clitoris%20cut%20from%20a%20girl%20subjected%20to%20female%20genital%20mutilation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20big%20chief%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20dominate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20small%20but%20charismatic%20fiftysomething%20from%20northwest%20Ivory%20Coast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20put%20it%20on%20my%20face%20and%20body%26quot%3B%20every%20three%20months%20or%20so%20%26quot%3Bfor%20about%20three%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Diallo%2C%20who%20asked%20AFP%20not%20to%20use%20his%20real%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenitalia%20cut%20from%20girls%20in%20illegal%20%26quot%3Bcircumcision%26quot%3B%20ceremonies%20is%20used%20in%20several%20regions%20of%20the%20West%20African%20country%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20love%20potions%26quot%3B%20or%20magic%20ointments%20that%20some%20believe%20will%20help%20them%20%26quot%3Bmake%20money%20or%20reach%20high%20political%20office%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Labe%20Gneble%2C%20head%20of%20the%20National%20Organisation%20for%20Women%2C%20Children%20and%20the%20Family%20(ONEF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20ground-down%20clitoris%20can%20sell%20for%20up%20to%20around%20%24170%20(152%20euros)%2C%20the%20equivalent%20of%20what%20many%20in%20Ivory%20Coast%20earn%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiallo%20stopped%20using%20the%20functions%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20but%20regional%20police%20chief%20Lieutenant%20N'Guessan%20Yosso%20confirmed%20to%20AFP%20that%20dried%20clitorises%20are%20still%20%26quot%3Bvery%20sought%20after%20for%20mystical%20practices%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20clear%20from%20extensive%20interviews%20AFP%20conducted%20with%20former%20faith%20healers%2C%20circumcisers%2C%20social%20workers%2C%20researchers%20and%20NGOs%2C%20that%20there%20is%20a%20thriving%20traffic%20in%20female%20genitalia%20for%20the%20powers%20they%20supposedly%20impart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20are%20convinced%20the%20trade%20is%20hampering%20the%20fight%20against%20female%20genital%20mutilation%20(FGM)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20banned%20in%20the%20religiously%20diverse%20nation%20for%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20century.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%2C%20one%20in%20five%20Ivorian%20women%20are%20still%20being%20cut%2C%20according%20to%20the%20OECD%2C%20with%20one%20in%20two%20being%20mutilated%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20north.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECut%20and%20mixed%20with%20plants%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20had%20a%20crisis%20of%20conscience%20and%20decided%20to%20campaign%20against%20FGM%2C%20Diallo%20said%20he%20was%20often%20asked%20by%20the%20women%20who%20performed%20excisions%20around%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Touba%20to%20use%20his%20powers%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20evil%20spells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFemale%20circumcision%20has%20been%20practised%20by%20different%20religions%20in%20West%20Africa%20for%20centuries%2C%20with%20most%20girls%20cut%20between%20childhood%20and%20adolescence.%20Many%20families%20consider%20it%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%20or%20a%20way%20to%20control%20and%20repress%20female%20sexuality%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20Children's%20agency%20UNICEF%2C%20which%20condemns%20cutting%20as%20a%20dangerous%20violation%20of%20girls'%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20physical%20and%20psychological%20pain%2C%20cutting%20can%20be%20fatal%2C%20and%20lead%20to%20sterility%2C%20birth%20complications%2C%20chronic%20infections%20and%20bleeding%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20loss%20of%20sexual%20pleasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiallo%20would%20often%20accompany%20the%20women%20who%20do%20the%20cutting%20out%20into%20the%20forest%20or%20to%20a%20home%20where%20dozens%20of%20girls%20would%20be%20circumcised%2C%20often%20surrounded%20by%20fetishes%20and%20sacred%20objects.%20So%20it%20was%20relatively%20easy%20for%20the%20former%20faith%20healer%20to%20obtain%20the%20precious%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20would%20cut%20the%20clitorises%20they%20would%20dry%20them%20for%20a%20month%20or%20two%20then%20pound%20them%20with%20stones%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bblack%20powder%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20then%20sometimes%20mixed%20with%20%26quot%3Bleaves%2C%20roots%20and%20bark%26quot%3B%20or%20shea%20butter%20that%20is%20often%20used%20in%20cosmetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20could%20then%20sell%20it%20for%20around%20%26quot%3B100%2C000%20CFA%20Francs%20(152%20euros)%20if%20the%20girl%20was%20a%20virgin%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3B65%2C000%20(99%20euros)%20if%20she%20already%20had%20a%20child%26quot%3B%20or%20barter%20it%20for%20goods%20and%20services%2C%20Diallo%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-witch%20doctor%20said%20he%20was%20able%20to%20get%20some%20of%20the%20powder%20recently%20--%20a%20mix%20of%20human%20flesh%20and%20plants%2C%20he%20believes%20--%20from%20a%20cutter%20in%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20was%20shown%20the%20powder%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20analyse%20it%20without%20buying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Organ%20trafficking'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20circumcisers%20interviewed%20by%20AFP%20insisted%20that%20clitorises%20cut%20from%20girls%20are%20either%20buried%2C%20thrown%20into%20a%20river%20or%20given%20to%20the%20parents%2C%20depending%20on%20local%20custom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20in%20the%20west%20of%20the%20country%20admitted%20some%20end%20up%20being%20used%20for%20magic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20pretend%20they%20are%20the%20girls'%20parents%20and%20go%20off%20with%20the%20clitoris%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitch%20doctors%20use%20them%20for%20%26quot%3Bincantations%26quot%3B%20and%20sell%20them%20afterwards%2C%20she%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20circumciser%20said%20some%20of%20her%20colleagues%20were%20complicit%20in%20the%20trade%2C%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20(genitalia)%20to%20people%20who%20are%20up%20to%20no%20good%26quot%3B%20for%20occult%20purposes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMutilated%20when%20she%20was%20still%20a%20child%2C%20one%20victim%20told%20AFP%20that%20her%20mother%20warned%20her%20to%20bring%20home%20the%20flesh%20that%20had%20been%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%20is%20regarded%20as%20%26quot%3Borgan%20trafficking%26quot%3B%20in%20Ivorian%20law%20and%20is%20punishable%20--%20like%20FGM%20--%20with%20fines%20and%20several%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20said%20lawyer%20Marie%20Laurence%20Didier%20Zeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20police%20in%20Odienne%2C%20who%20are%20in%20charge%20of%20five%20regions%20in%20the%20country's%20northwest%2C%20said%20no%20one%20has%20ever%20been%20indicted%20for%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20won't%20say%20anything%20about%20sacred%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20lamented%20Lieutenant%20N'Guessan%20Yosso.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cutters%20themselves%20are%20both%20feared%20and%20respected%2C%20locals%20told%20AFP%2C%20often%20seen%20as%20prisoners%20of%20evil%20spirits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Just%20nuts'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20clitoris%20cannot%20give%20you%20magical%20powers%2C%20it's%20just%20nuts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20gynaecologist%20Jacqueline%20Chanine%20based%20in%20the%20country's%20commercial%20capital%20Abidjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20practice%20is%20still%20stubbornly%20widespread%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDieudonne%20Kouadio%2C%20an%20anthropologist%20specialising%20in%20health%2C%20was%20presented%20with%20a%20box%20of%20the%20powder%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Odienne%2C%20150%20kilometres%20north%20of%20Touba.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20contained%20a%20dried%20cut%20organ%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20blackish%20powder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20discovery%20was%20included%20in%20a%202021%20report%20for%20the%20Djigui%20Foundation%2C%20whose%20conclusions%20were%20accepted%20by%20the%20Ministry%20for%20Women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20in%20Denguele%20district%2C%20of%20which%20Odienne%20is%20a%20part%2C%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20clitorises%20and%20mix%20the%20powder%20with%20their%20seeds%20to%20increase%20the%20fertility%20of%20their%20fields%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Nouho%20Konate%2C%20a%20Djigui%20foundation%20member%20who%20has%20been%20fighting%20FGM%20in%20the%20area%20for%2016%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20parents%20of%20young%20girls%20were%20%26quot%3Bgutted%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20told%20them%20of%20the%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20south%20and%20in%20the%20centre%20west%20of%20the%20country%2C%20women%20use%20clitoris%20powder%20as%20an%20aphrodisiac%2C%20hoping%20to%20prevent%20their%20husbands%20from%20straying%2C%20said%20criminologist%20Safie%20Roseline%20N'da%2C%20author%20of%20a%202023%20study%20on%20FGM%20which%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20two%20co-authors%20discovered%20that%20blood%20from%20cut%20women%20was%20also%20being%20used%20to%20honour%20traditional%20gods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20far%20from%20the%20only%20Ivorian%20folk%20remedies%20that%20use%20body%20parts%2C%20according%20to%20lawyer%20Didier%20Zeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMystic%20beliefs%20keep%20it%20going%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mystic%20has%20a%20central%20place%20in%20daily%20life%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Ivory%20Coast%20--%20where%20Islam%2C%20Christianity%20and%20traditional%20animist%20beliefs%20co-exist%20--%20said%20the%20Canadian%20anthropologist%20Boris%20Koenig%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20occult%20practices%20there.%20%26quot%3BIt%20touches%20every%20sphere%20of%20people's%20social%2C%20professional%2C%20family%20and%20love%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20there%20is%20generally%20nothing%20illegal%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%2C%20however%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20FGM%20survives%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Ivory%20Coast%2C%20NGOs%20argue%2C%20where%20the%20rate%20of%20cutting%20is%20generally%20falling%20and%20is%20below%20the%20West%20African%20average%20of%2028%20per%20cent%2C%20according%20to%20the%20OECD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20near%20Touba%2C%20the%20former%20witch%20doctor%20Diallo%20recalled%20how%20up%20to%2030%20women%20would%20be%20cut%20in%20a%20day%20in%20the%20places%20his%20magic%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dry%20season%20between%20January%20to%20March%20was%20the%20favoured%20period%20for%20circumcisions%20when%20the%20hot%20Harmattan%20wind%20from%20the%20Sahara%20helps%20scars%20heal%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStaff%20at%20the%20region's%20only%20social%20work%20centre%20say%20the%20cutting%20is%20still%20going%20on%20but%20is%20hard%20to%20quantify%20because%20it%20never%20happens%20in%20the%20open.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20goes%20on%20in%20secret%2C%20hidden%20behind%20traditional%20festivals%20which%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20practice%2C%20kept%20going%20they%20say%20by%20circumcisers%20from%20neighbouring%20Guinea%20--%20only%20a%20few%20kilometres%20away%20--%20where%20FGM%20rates%20are%20over%2090%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726030860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fo0kfa5og_ivory-coast-fgm-_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgirl-genitalia-mutilated-sold-for-magic-in-ivory-coast-6538386%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20he%20was%20a%20witch%20doctor%2C%20Moussa%20Diallo%20would%20regularly%20smear%20himself%20in%20a%20lotion%20made%20from%20a%20clitoris%20cut%20from%20a%20girl%20subjected%20to%20female%20genital%20mutilation.%22%